def: A New Zealand forest tree (Metrosideros robusta), also, itshard dark red wood, used by the Maoris for paddles and war clubs.
Of a color between white and brown. Pegge.
Wearing a cravat.The young men faultlessly appointed, handsomely cravatted. Thackeray.
Having the form of a mammilla.
Nonsecretion or defective secretion of urine; ischury.
A body of soldiers armed with rifles.
